    async def _run(
        self,
        function,
        *args,
        nanny: bool = False,
        workers: list[str] | None = None,
        wait: bool = True,
        on_error: Literal["raise", "return", "ignore"] = "raise",
        **kwargs,
    ):

                wait=wait,
